reviews.review_text: Recording Source We would've been using Jim's or my Neumann KM140's into my Aerco p/s. The gear listed was Keith Litzenberger's at the time? Many years ago! Maybe we did you Keith's gear? I'd have to dig out the tapes or my old list to check what source my Master is
End of a era  Days between exemplified this concert. As a witness, I can report Jerry Garcia shed tears during Days Between. Sad tidings indeed.
